{"tid":1631504,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"希望記者幫問以下問題,謝謝","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:11.000Z","uid":115769,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b405d8c1ef57fc19a03e4144b25230055d7c9e28","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"1. 警察覺得鐳射筆係傷害到人, 咁每次警察用電筒照記者, 又係咩做法<br />\n另外,咁樣亦都影響係camera 面前既觀眾, 佢地除左眼睛會感到唔舒服, 亦同時睇唔到現場發生咩事, 其實係咪警方唔想俾市民知道發生緊咩事呢?<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察要蒙面, 幾乎只係見到對眼, 有大部份直情連眼都遮埋, 咁係咩原因呢? 因為唔想有人認到佢地? 咁唔見得人既原因係咩? 而且李家超有講過每個警察都有好清楚既號碼可以識別,可唔可以係呢到詳細講解下係邊到可以搵到同點識別<br />\n<br />\n3. 警方多次係市民咩裝備都無既情況下發放催淚彈, 咁政府又唔俾人帶口睪或gears去保護自己,<br />\n係咪即係市民只可以啞忍去接受你地警方既暴力虐待?<br />\n<br />\n4. 見到有警察係橋上各橋下既示威者掉垃圾桶,係咪計劃既一部份? 定係該名警員巳失控? <br />\n<br />\n5. 見到有警員扮示威者打爛店鋪物品, 又有警員10月6號扮示威者各記者掉汽油彈之後上左警車, 可唔可以有解釋呢"},{"pid":"e3a47b12b1231f3cb293bf45b4816a80b702df37","tid":1631504,"uid":294083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631437/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非同我入！！！"},{"pid":"061c004a1badb69e65023cfbba86b28a94be193c","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"779bddbda7f6f4bc4bf55aac74474b577b6e684b","tid":1631504,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6f6cad84b6022c33e27ec2cbed108a82969b1cc","tid":1631504,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d1305b89a27a23d057618289553ae277c01b6115","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7d71dc2185d4e3376953ca04298e8bc14725439","tid":1631504,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:43.000Z","msg":"【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"0dc56333ca7cecfb7c53cac0bf375060d6602bd3","tid":1631504,"uid":87305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a368a4f02403284191c13e2ccfdcf3f75d32b023","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4e3b33ecd5c353c0c82becf0403acb24f5bf5df2","tid":1631504,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba9152fbd4aab10f71e811334b632937c161b942","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e47e1cb193695bbb97b121a460d1806a0e3aef59","tid":1631504,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78bb52c42b8cfa13860e8b467f8746c1586801d3","tid":1631504,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非戰場－面具人鏈</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外國嘅人好幸福，一出世就生活係民主國家，有部分人根本唔會明點解我地爭取民主要用裝修、神獸（唔好高估外國人嘅智力，佢地睇野好表面）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有位巴講得好啱，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之所以漸漸少咗國際支持，係因為和理非戰場越來越細</span></span>。冇和理非嘅活動吸引佢地嘅眼球，餘下嘅只有神獸同裝修。<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，我地可以搞返個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">面具人鏈</span></span>，表達我地不畏反蒙面法，不畏極權嘅精神。<br />\n人鏈活動一直都比較少人被人拉，比起遊行更適合一家大細出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"},{"pid":"13912e9c3b5ac7462250297d346d32efb85a97cc","tid":1631504,"uid":115769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"Push"}